claim.claim-text:
A battery pack (100) comprising:
a rechargeable battery module (110);
a battery management system (120) for controlling charging/discharging of the battery module (110);
wherein the battery module (110) comprises a substantially linear charging and discharging voltage-time profile within at least part of the charging and discharging cycle of the battery module (110);
wherein the battery management system (120) is arranged to calculate a state of charge of the battery module (110) by using the linear charging/discharging characteristics of the battery module (110).

A power apparatus for an idle stop and go system for starting an engine, comprising:
a battery pack (100) according to any one of claims 1 to 12;
a power generating module (210) for charging the battery module (110);
a starter motor (220) arranged to be powered by the discharge of the battery module (110).
